{"tid":1277062,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"近排愛上了灰色衫","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T16:28:32.000Z","uid":227650,"like":7,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b1256177912086a3d78390b04131b9631370c1","tid":1277062,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVWqMSR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVWqMSR.jpg&h=fb40bd75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rJkAMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rJkAMe.jpg&h=2e02fb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEQnO6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEQnO6h.jpg&h=de70f259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解釋，總之就係覺得係一種好正嘅顏色 同埋好特別嘅顏色。<br />\n<br />\n記得喺某個網站度睇到兩句對灰色嘅評論，我覺得都值得參考;所以成句copy咗過嚟:<br />\n<br />\n「白＋灰：灰色搭配明亮的白色就會擔任暗色的角色」<br />\n<br />\n「灰＋黑：但是當灰色搭配黑色，又會擔任提亮的角色！」<br />\n<br />\n我覺得仲有一個特別之處係同白色、黑色相比，灰色有深灰、淺灰;亦都可以做到唔同嘅效果出嚟。"},{"pid":"50002ae8004a06bfc03b78427d8f1ca3ee3a0dba","tid":1277062,"uid":227650,"like":1,"dislike":82,"score":-81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"咁著幾好 <br />\n<br />\np.s 個男仔幾靚仔，可能引到連登基佬出嚟<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3jWeFk9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jWeFk9.jpg&h=08d5c0fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e0149c26d633efdbef9c15375018696e9cb0fa6","tid":1277062,"uid":260253,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"不過天氣熱成身汗好顯眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c17cb292bda3fea0eea99800a591f41feb071a","tid":1277062,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"1e0149c26d633efdbef9c15375018696e9cb0fa6","tid":1277062,"uid":260253,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"不過天氣熱成身汗好顯眼<img src=\"/assets/faces