By":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會考慮深灰色？"},{"pid":"11a0e795a172b937adf42f4bdb3d458b683083c5","tid":1277062,"uid":68777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:31:09.000Z","msg":"灰襯灰嘅代表人物<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwLb2jV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwLb2jV.png&h=5d0c0cab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e5793c1b54466463b722136bd4a5b849fba5d95","tid":1277062,"uid":171856,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a7b1256177912086a3d78390b04131b9631370c1","tid":1277062,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVWqMSR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVWqMSR.jpg&h=fb40bd75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rJkAMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rJkAMe.jpg&h=2e02fb9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEQnO6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEQnO6h.jpg&h=de70f259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解釋，總之就係覺得係一種好正嘅顏色 同埋好特別嘅顏色。<br />\n<br />\n記得喺某個網站度睇到兩句對灰色嘅評論，我覺得都值得參考;所以成句copy咗過嚟:<br />\n<br />\n「白＋灰：灰色搭配明亮的白色就會擔任暗色的角色」<br />\n<br />\n「灰＋黑：但是當灰色搭配黑色，又會擔任提亮的角色！」<br />\n<br />\n我覺得仲有一個特別之處係同白色、黑色相比，灰色有深灰、淺灰;亦都可以做到唔同嘅效果出嚟。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:52:47.000Z","msg":"留意左幾個POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想知道六尺巴打平時實際著衫係咩效果<br />\n純粹係因為巴打每次都用鬼佬做例子<br />\n想睇下香港人咁著會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85de54bf47e9b57d20aadbc1a64e7b6127ed8fa1","tid":1277062,"uid":274276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:53:34.000Z","msg":"一出汗就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"